{"tid":1588688,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"加利仔質疑曼聯　仲要使幾多錢？","createTime":"2019-09-23T02:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T07:26:32.000Z","uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b702fca17099fca75e49630fb38a5addac1d4afd","tid":1588688,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:36:00.000Z","msg":"曼聯今輪又輸波，令好多人都唔耐煩，猛問幾時先睇得番一隊似樣啲嘅紅魔鬼，為曼聯作客韋斯咸現場評述嘅名宿加利尼維利都好不滿，佢質問曼聯高層：「重建曼聯仲要使幾錢？」<br />\n<br />\n加利仔指出：「大家諗吓，曼聯近年花費重建球隊使咗幾多錢，接近9億鎊，已經係天文數字，但球隊毫無重心。」<br />\n<br />\n「我哋重要使幾多錢，先至令曼聯重返以前水平？3億？4億？定係5億鎊？呢班球員冇特別，唔夠水平及特點，統統未準備好。」<br />\n<br />\n加利仔：曼聯要買華拉尼簡迪麥巴比<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.goal.com/zh-hk/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%8A%A0%E5%88%A9%E4%BB%94-%E6%9B%BC%E8%81%AF-%E8%A6%81-%E8%B2%B7-%E8%8F%AF%E6%8B%89%E5%B0%BC-%E7%B0%A1%E8%BF%AA-%E9%BA%A5%E5%B7%B4%E6%AF%94/zqdd2yn302jg1eijuqf47xirb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goal.com%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%2588%25A9%25E4%25BB%2594-%25E6%259B%25BC%25E8%2581%25AF-%25E8%25A6%2581-%25E8%25B2%25B7-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%258B%2589%25E5%25B0%25BC-%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E8%25BF%25AA-%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E6%25AF%2594%2Fzqdd2yn302jg1eijuqf47xirb&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8ulywV2WuQOZSh7uXaWrws9Zz8%3D&h=a724be25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.goal.com/zh-hk/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%8A%A0%E5%88%A9%E4%BB%94-%E6%9B%BC%E8%81%AF-%E8%A6%81-%E8%B2%B7-%E8%8F%AF%E6%8B%89%E5%B0%BC-%E7%B0%A1%E8%BF%AA-%E9%BA%A5%E5%B7%B4%E6%AF%94/zqdd2yn302jg1eijuqf47xirb</a></span><br />\n<br />\n加利仔：曼聯重組要使更多錢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20190430/bkn-20190430031159074-0430_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20190430%2Fbkn-20190430031159074-0430_00882_001.html&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8ulywV2WuQOZSh7uXaWrws9Zz8%3D&h=843b9822\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/2019043